varargs make_obj(string sFile, int iHowMany)

  An lfun defined for all objects inheriting CLONE, which includes rooms
  and monsters. Clones up to iHowMany objects into the calling object,
  making sure to count how many objects are already cloned as to not
  exceed iHowMany. iHowMany is optional. When not specificied, it will
  default to 1.

  Example: 
           make_obj("/obj/goblin", 4);
           make_obj("/obj/wolf");

See also: make_and_equip, make_limited_obj, make_unique_obj, 
          clone_object
          
